title: Sample Book, Fresh 'n' Fanciful, 1963–64
description: Covered with black oil cloth, printed with white daisies and title. Contains 26 hand printed wallpaper samples, among them 5 taken by Beryl Austrian from CUM originals: Swirl, Medallion, Josephine, Basket Weave, Sutton Place.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Fresh 'n' Fanciful, 1963–64; Designed by Beryl S. Austrian (American, 1899–1982); USA; screen-printed on paper; 37 x 49 cm (14 9/16 x 19 5/16 in.); 1963-84-1-1/97
